    <div class="text">
      <h1 class="banner-h1 cool-font">Send Gifts<span class=""> To Foster Kids</span></h1>
      <h4 class="quick-font pb-1 hide">Every child should feel valued, remembered, and loved</h4>
      <h4 class="quick-font pb-1 hide">
        Donate holiday & birthday gifts to the kids who may not otherwise get one
