  <div class="custom-wrapper" id="about">
    <div class="custom-row">
      <div class="custom-col custom-left">
        <img src="/public/img/kids-cover.jpg" alt="donation drop off near me" class="grn-box" />
      </div>
      <div class="custom-col custom-right">
        <h4 id="grn-font" class="crayon-font font-lg">We Need Your Help</h4>
        <p id="left-align" class="subtext quick-font">
          500,000+ kids spend time in foster care each year. 
          And 4.2M+ youth are homeless in the U.S.
          For many of them, Christmas time can be sad and lonely because they are undergoing
          stressful situations. With your generosity and kindness, we are able to provide a moment
          of happiness to the kids who are in crisis. By creating this platform, we wish to
          provide effortless and convenient ways to share the joy of the holidays.<br />
          Your gifts make it possible to bring happiness to the kids.
        </p>
        <p class="quick-font">Got any questions? We would love to hear from you.</p>
        <a href="/about"><button type="button" class="quick-font wishcard-btn grn-btn" id="btn1">
            How To Contact Us
          </button></a>
